import java.util.Scanner;
class DPC207n107
{
    public static void main(String arg[])throws Exception
    {
        int a,b,c,d,w,x,y,z,t;
        Scanner in=new Scanner(System.in);
        t=in.nextInt();
        while(t-->0)
        {
            a=in.nextInt();
            b=in.nextInt();
            c=in.nextInt();
            d=in.nextInt();
            w=in.nextInt();
            x=in.nextInt();
            y=in.nextInt();
            z=in.nextInt();
            if(Math.pow((c-a),2)+Math.pow((d-b),2)!=Math.pow((y-w),2)+Math.pow((z-x),2))
            {
                System.out.println(Math.max(a,w)+" "+Math.max(b,x)+" "+Math.min(c,y)+" "+Math.min(d,z));
            }
            else
                System.out.println("No Overlap");
        }
    }
}
